<DATELINE>STOCKHOLM, Sweden (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Sweden's attorney general has decided
against prosecuting a magazine for defamation after it quoted the
wife of former Swedish tennis great Bjorn Borg as saying, ``Swedes
are stupid nobodies.''
   The remark attributed to Loredana Borg, a former Italian rock
singer who married Borg in September, appeared on the advertising
